<item>
            <title>[SPARK-10172] History Server web UI gets messed up when sorting on any column</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-10172</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If the history web UI displays the &quot;Attempt ID&quot; column, when clicking the table header to sort on any column, the entire page gets messed up.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This seems to be a problem with the sorttable.js not able to correctly handle tables with rowspan.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
